sample_comments.text:
I booked Suite with sea view and balcony:
Pluses
* amazing view from the room;
* clean;
* staff were very helpful;

Minuses
* needs renovation, the floor is full of holes, the railings are peeling, rusted;
* hotel don't use hand soap! So had to use shampoo & shower gel, which are not antibacterial;
* it was the first hotel where I saw a mouse;

So the price is a bit too high for the room's condition (pictures were from 6 years ago, when the hotel was built), but staff were friendly and helpful and view from room - amazing.
